# Problem-space-Project
This project is done as part of TAPMI LEAD course.
Grasshoper is an US multinational retailer with headquarters in Illinois. It has stores in 5 states across US and is the market leader in Grocery and General Merchandise products

The Business Planning team of Grasshoper is responsible for creating business plans and forecasts, that will increase the visibility and sales of the retail chain, thereby optimizing General Merchandise budget for next fiscal year. The head of this team has been approached by Mu Sigma and they are looking to build trust by showcasing their capabilities. 
We will be effectively calculating the forecasts of Sports department for next fiscal year, as per Client targets. 
